<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=0, minimal-ui">
    <meta name="keywords" content="系统开发中,后台模板,后台管理系统,光年HTML模板">
    <meta name="description" content="系统正在开发中，即将上线，敬请期待！">
    <meta name="author" content="yinq">
    <title>系统开发中 - 光年(Light Year Admin V5)后台管理系统模板</title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="favicon.ico">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    <meta name="apple-touch-fullscreen" content="yes">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="default">
    <link href="css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="css/materialdesignicons.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="css/style.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-image: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.1), rgba(255,255,255,1) 85%), radial-gradient(ellipse at top left, rgba(13,110,253,0.2), transparent 50%), radial-gradient(ellipse at top right, rgba(255,193,7,0.2), transparent 50%), radial-gradient(ellipse at center right, rgba(111,66,193,0.2), transparent 50%), radial-gradient(ellipse at center left, rgba(214,51,132,0.2), transparent 50%);
            background-attachment: fixed;
            background-size: cover;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
        }

        [data-theme|='translucent'],
        [data-theme|='dark'] {
            background: transparent;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .maintenance-page {
            height: 100%;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .maintenance-body {
            padding-top: 5%;
        }

        .maintenance-icon {
            font-size: 120px;
            color: rebeccapurple;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        @@keyframes pulse {
            0%

        {
            transform: scale(1);
        }

        50% {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        100% {
            transform: scale(1);
        }

        }

        .maintenance-title {
            font-size: 48px;
            line-height: 1.2;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .maintenance-subtitle {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .progress-container {
            margin: 30px 0;
            width: 70%;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        .progress-bar {
            height: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background-color: #e0e0e0;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .progress {
            height: 100%;
            background-color: rebeccapurple;
            border-radius: 5px;
            width: 0%;
            transition: width 3s ease-in-out;
        }

            .progress.complete {
                width: 100%;
            }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #ff9800;
            border-color: #ff9800;
            padding: 10px 30px;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

            .btn-primary:hover {
                background-color: #f57c00;
                border-color: #f57c00;
                transform: translateY(-2px);
                box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(255, 152, 0, 0.4);
            }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <section class="maintenance-page">
        <div class="maintenance-body text-center">
            <div class="maintenance-icon">
                <i class="mdi mdi-progress-clock"></i>
            </div>
            <h1 class="maintenance-title">系统开发中</h1>
            <h5 class="maintenance-subtitle">我们的技术团队正在全力开发中，功能即将上线！</h5>

            <div class="progress-container">
                <div class="progress-bar">
                    <div class="progress" id="progressBar"></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p class="text-muted mb-5">请稍后再来访问，或返回首页查看其他内容。</p>

        </div>
    </section>

    <script src="js/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script>
        // 页面加载完成后执行
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            const progressBar = document.getElementById('progressBar');

            // 模拟进度加载
            setTimeout(function() {
                progressBar.classList.add('complete');
            }, 3000); // 3秒后完成加载
        });


    </script>
</body>
</html>
